                    div(class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 feature text-center")
                        i(class="fa fa-desktop" )
                        div(class="feature-content")
                            h5 Clean Design
                            p Scheduly is simple and beautiful. A clean user interface lets you focus on getting things done for the day. 

                    div(class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 feature text-center")
                        i(class="fa fa-calendar")
                        div(class="feature-content")
                            h5 Smart Scheduling
                            p Put away tasks that you plan to do later by setting reminders or adding task dependencies. This keeps your todo list organized and distraction-free.
                    div(class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 feature text-center")
                        i(class="fa fa-refresh")
                        div(class="feature-content")
                            h5 Recurring Tasks
                            p Add recurring tasks to your todo list so that you won't forget. When the time comes, Scheduly has your back!

                    div.col-sm-12
                        br
                        br
                        br

                    div(class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 feature text-center")
                        i(class="fa fa-list-ol")
                        div(class="feature-content")
                            h5 Easy to Prioritize
                            p Automatically track each task's deadline and priority. Tasks are sorted intuitively so that you can concentrate on what's important.

                    div(class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 feature text-center")
                        i(class="fa fa-pencil")
                        div(class="feature-content")
                            h5 Track Your Progress
                            p View completed tasks and daily highlights in your archive. Be proud of all the things you accomplish each day!

                    div(class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 feature text-center")
                        i(class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up")
                        div(class="feature-content")
                            h5 Positive Attitude
                            p Stay motivated by thinking good thoughts. Scheduly is here to support you through each step of the day.


        section(id="signup")
            div(class="container")
                div(class="row")
                    br
                    br
                    br

                    div(class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 text-center")
                        i(class="fa fa-pencil-square-o margin-20")
                        h2(class="black") Sign Up
                        br
                        br
                        div(class="row")
                            div(class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3")
                                form#signupform(role="form" method='POST' action='/users/signup')
                                    div.form-group
                                        label.form-control-label(for="first_name" style="display:inline; padding:0px; margin-right:0") First Name
                                        input#first_name.form-control(type="text" name="first_name" style="display:inline" required)
                                    div.form-group
                                        label.form-control-label(for="last_name" style="display:inline; padding:0px; margin-right:0") Last Name
                                        input#last_name.form-control(type="text" name="last_name" style="display:inline" required)
                                    div.form-group
                                        label.form-control-label(for="email" style="display:inline; padding:0px; margin-right:0") Email
                                        input#email.form-control(type="email" name="email" style="display:inline" required)
                                    div.form-group
                                        label.form-control-label(for="username" style="display:inline; padding:0px; margin-right:0") Username
                                        input#username1.form-control(type="text" name="username" style="display:inline" required)
                                    div.form-group
                                        label.form-control-label(for="password" style="display:inline; padding:0px; margin-right:0") Password
                                        input#password1.form-control(type="password" name="password" style="display:inline" required)
                                    br
                                    button#signupbutton(type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-primary-initial btn-md btn-submit" style="font-size:12px; padding: 12px 16px") Sign Up


